2007 05 08
First public release!  Yay!

2007 06 10
You can now pass options as a Hash.
You can specify default sort direction with :sort_direction in 'add_to_sortable_params' and 'sortable_order'.
Removed controller name from sortable data key (allows sort solutions to be used across multiple controllers).

2007 06 18
Fixed bug with aliasing fields.
